<br>
sometimes the xp bubbles are a bit buggy.  Especially near the beginning or end of a bubble.<br>
<br>
dunno why, it just has always seemed that way.  An hour really isnt' a very significant amount of pull time... I'd say go back and do that same spot for 5 or so hours and you would have a much better average...<br>
<br>
if it was still the ratio of 12/16 blue to 1/16 blue after 5 hours, i would say there is an issue... but, with only an hour of sample time... You can't really chalk that up as being anything significant.<br>
